<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui" 
	xmlns:mn='urn:import:mindnotes.client.ui'
	xmlns:txt='urn:import:mindnotes.client.ui.text'>
	<ui:style>
		
		.sidebar {
			padding: 12px;
			min-width: 266px;
		}
		
		.sidebar p {
			text-align: justify;		
		}
		
		.header {
						
			margin-bottom: 12px;
			
		}
		
		.header-h1 {
			margin-top: 0px;
			margin-left: 12px;
			font-size: 28px;
			font-weight: bold;
		}
		
		.toprightlinks {
			padding: 12px;
			text-align: right;
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #eee;
		}
		
		.toprightlinks a {
			color: #eee;
		}
		
		.topbutton {
			cursor: pointer;

			margin-left: 12px;
			text-decoration: underline;
		}
		
		.topbar {
			background: #222228;
			color: #fffaf1;
			width: 100%;
		}
		
		.title {
			padding: 10px 12px 12px 24px;
			font-weight:bold;
			color: #eee;
			font-size: large;
		}

		
	</ui:style>
	<g:DockLayoutPanel unit='PX' ui:field="dockLayoutPanel">
		<g:north size='40'>
			<g:HorizontalPanel addStyleNames="{style.topbar}">
				<g:HTMLPanel addStyleNames="{style.header}">
					<span class="{style.header-h1}">
						Mind Notes
						<span style="font-size: 21px">(28.07.2010)</span>
					</span>
					<g:InlineLabel ui:field="titleLabel" addStyleNames="{style.title}" />
				</g:HTMLPanel>
				<g:FlowPanel addStyleNames="{style.header} {style.toprightlinks}" ui:field="cloudBarPanel">
					<g:InlineLabel ui:field="greetLabel"></g:InlineLabel>
					<g:Anchor ui:field="newButton" addStyleNames="{style.topbutton}">New</g:Anchor>
					<g:Anchor ui:field="loadButton" addStyleNames="{style.topbutton}">Load</g:Anchor>
					<g:Anchor ui:field="saveButton" addStyleNames="{style.topbutton}">Save to cloud</g:Anchor>						
					<g:Anchor ui:field="saveLocalButton" addStyleNames="{style.topbutton}">Save locally</g:Anchor>
					<g:Anchor ui:field="logoutLink" addStyleNames="{style.topbutton}">Log out</g:Anchor>

				</g:FlowPanel>

			</g:HorizontalPanel>

		</g:north>
		<g:center>
			
			<g:SplitLayoutPanel>
			<g:west size='266'>
			<g:ScrollPanel>
				<g:HTMLPanel>
					<div class="{style.sidebar}">
						<p><a href="http://code.google.com/p/mind-notes/source/checkout" target="_blank">View source</a><br />
						<a href="http://code.google.com/p/mind-notes/issues/list" target="_blank">Report a bug</a><br />
						<a href="http://code.google.com/p/mind-notes/issues/list" target="_blank">Propose a feature</a></p>
					
						<h2>Iteration 3</h2>
						<p>
							<strong>Cloud Storage</strong>
						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>The app now requires Google Accounts login; you should see your
							email in the top right corner.</li>
							<li>Try making your own mind map and click "Save to cloud"</li>
							<li>Make some changes or reload the page, then click "Load from cloud"</li>
						</ul>
						<p>
							<strong>App Cache</strong>
						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>The app can be loaded and used without an internet connection.
							Try disconnecting from the internet and then hitting refresh.</li>
							<li>Notice the cloud features are disabled now.</li>
						</ul>
						<h2>Iteration 2</h2>
					<p><strong>Better Layout, Undo Stack, Rich Text Formatting, Copy/Paste</strong></p>
					<ul>
					<li>The nodes are now positioned on an AbsolutePanel, and their positions are calculated
					by the script. Left-hand side and right-hand sides are now supported.</li>
					<li>After adding or deleting nodes, try undoing this (ctrl+z)</li>
					<li>Nodes now can be edited using rich text editing. You can play with the B-I-U buttons, or paste some text from another webpage.</li>
					<li>Try cutting (ctrl+x) and pasting (ctrl+v) nodes around. Copy is not implemented yet.</li>
					<li>I abandoned the idea of porting this to SVG, because current method works well enough.</li>
					</ul>
					
					</div>
					
				</g:HTMLPanel>
			</g:ScrollPanel>
			</g:west>
			<g:center>
				<mn:MindMapWidget ui:field="mindMapWidget"></mn:MindMapWidget>
			</g:center>
			</g:SplitLayoutPanel>
		</g:center>

	</g:DockLayoutPanel>

</ui:UiBinder> 